    <assets>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko682.00">
            <value key="en">Donko! You did it!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko682.01">
            <value key="en">You saved Pac-Man, AND the school!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko682.02">
            <value key="en">That’ll be amazing on your resume! I’m SO JEALOUS...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko683.00">
            <value key="en">Oh! Well, ${slot:playerName} helped too-</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko684.00">
            <value key="en">YEAHHH! Donko, you’re good at EVERYTHING!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko685.00">
            <value key="en">Well, but it was really, like, a joint effort-</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko686.00">
            <value key="en">WELL DONE DONKO.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko686.01">
            <value key="en">GALAGA IS PLEASED!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko687.00">
            <value key="en">...Everyone’s giving me all the credit!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko687.01">
            <value key="en">It’s like, totally unfair!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko688.00">
            <value key="en">Heh… I don’t mind.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko688.01">
            <value key="en">After all… everybody knows you here.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko689.00">
            <value key="en">I’m not as popular as you, so they don’t notice me as much…</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko689.01">
            <value key="en">But I don’t really care.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko689.02">
            <value key="en">The only person I care about being popular with is you.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko690.00">
            <value key="en">OMG, ${slot:playerName}...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko690.01">
            <value key="en">If you keep saying corny stuff like that around me...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko690.02">
            <value key="en">You’re gonna like, totally ruin my reputation!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko691.00">
            <value key="en">(I don’t care about popularity…</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko691.01">
            <value key="en">Or fashion…</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko691.02">
            <value key="en">Or even about music. I just listen to what’s on the radio!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko692.00">
            <value key="en">But I do care about Donko… I care about her a lot.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko692.01">
            <value key="en">And if those things are important to her, I know they really matter.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko693.00">
            <value key="en">From here on out, I’ll take her feelings seriously.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko693.01">
            <value key="en">She deserves it.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko694.00">
            <value key="en">...Darn, I wish I could’ve thought of a drum pun to sneak in there…</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko694.01">
            <value key="en">That would have been perfect.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko694.02">
            <value key="en">Per(cussion)fect?!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_sdonko695.00">
            <value key="en">...Nailed it.)</value>
        </TextAsset>
    </assets>
